## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `openssl-sys` build error | `apt install pkg-config libssl-dev` (Ubuntu) / `brew install openssl` (macOS) |
| `Lemonade Server not available` error | Run `lemonade-server serve` — server on `localhost:13305` is auto-discovered; `LEMONADE_URL` only needed for non-default URLs |
| Transcription error on first call | Model not loaded yet — first call triggers load; retry, or check `GET /api/v1/health` |
| `transcribe()` returns error: "Could not open audio data" | Empty or corrupt audio bytes passed to provider |
| `TranscriptionManager::try_new_auto` fails without server | No server on `localhost:13305` and `LEMONADE_URL` not set — construction is sync so this is a URL-resolution error, not a connectivity error |
| Schema not found | Check `$UFORGE_SCHEMA_DIR`, verify `.json` files exist |
| Dimension mismatch (future sqlite-vec) | Ensure embedding model matches vector column dimensions |
| `database is locked` | Only one writer at a time; check for stale processes holding `knowledge.db` |
| Tests fail after adding SQLite column | Run `cargo test` against a fresh `TempDir` — tests never share state |